       Name: Cognitive Flush
       Kind: Spell
     Target: TAR_CHAR_NOTSELF
   Position: POS_FIGHTING
   Min Mana: 15
 Wait Beats: 12
 Can Learn: TRUE
Noun Damage: None
   Wear-Off: !Cognitive Flush!
Acquisition:
   - Psionicist: level 50
Description:
   Cognitive Flush is an advanced Psionicist offensive ability that strips
   magical buffs from a target by overwhelming their mental defenses with a
   broad-spectrum psionic disruption. The Psionicist broadcasts a diffuse
   wave of mental static that interferes with the cognitive processes
   maintaining the target's magical protections, causing them to unravel.

   Cognitive Flush functions similarly to a Dispel Magic, but is focused
   specifically on a single opponent (not the room) and is delivered through
   psionic means. The flush is particularly effective against psychic and
   mental buffs, as these share the cognitive substrate the Psionicist
   is disrupting. It is a targeted depuff tool that Psionicists use to
   strip protected opponents before launching their main assault.
*******************************************************************************
